      "full_name": "ACE Electronic HK Co., Limited",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "ACE Electronic HK Co., Limited (“ACE Electronic”) is an entity registered in Hong Kong that supplies electronic components to Russian industries, including the military industry. Some of the company’s partners are military-industrial companies themselves, such as CJSC “NPF ‘Micran’”, which produces combat control systems. Other of the company’s partners, such as LLC NPK Fotonika, act as intermediaries supplying components to military-industrial companies. Due to the high consumption of military products, Russia’s military industry is dependent on imports of semiconductors and other electronic components. Since the imposition of Union restrictive measures prohibiting the export of various electronic components to Russia, ACE Electronic is actively involved in providing Russia-based recipients with electronic components, including semiconductor devices.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}